description.content:
AllRide Apps - Award-Winning Ecommerce Websites & Apps with Delivery Features 


I am the CEO of "AllRide Apps" (Google it).


Looking for an expert eCommerce team to develop and maintain your eCommerce website and apps? Trust the team that:


  • Developed eCommerce solutions for retail, grocery, fashion, books, electronics & many more businesses
  • Developed multiple Award-Winning apps in the last 10 years
  • Worked with 60+ multi-million dollar companies and 500+ startups to launch their products, get millions of users & secure funding
  • Provided an unparalleled customer service


Here's what you get with our eCommerce Solutions:


  1. Native iOS and Android Apps
  2. Ecommerce Website & API (Custom, Shopify, Magento, WooCommerce)
  3. Premium theme-based customized website
  4. Inventory Panel + Business Admin Panel
  5. Customer App (Optional)


Do you need delivery too?


We have a complete Delivery Management System with a Delivery Manager Panel and Apps for Delivery Boys (iOS + Android)


Extra features


  • Multiple payment options + COD
  • Multi-language
  • AWS server setup (We are a trusted AWS partner)
  • 1-month FREE bug support


Contact me to see the demo.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is this Gig price for any type of eCommerce development
questionsAndAnswers.answer: This gig pricing is specifically for Magento, as we have the complete solution and most modules ready for Magento. Magento 2.x is Adobe acquired and is the most trusted eCommerce engine in the world. However, we can surely work on any other type of eCommerce tool and customize it for your needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer any monthly subscription?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we do! Our subscription plans start from $179/month with flexible monthly and annual payment plans. Our plans are task-based and appropriate for businesses of all sizes. We also provide customized plans to suit your specific business needs. Send us a message to see & learn more about our plans.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What will I get in the Basic package?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The basic package is our SaaS-based monthly subscription pricing solution. The price starts from as low as $179/month. - Website & admin panels - Delivery boy apps - Delivery Management System You can have many options as add-on features like - Own branded apps - Integrations - Analytics
